    "title": "Quotient vector spaces",
    "section": "",
    "text": "Let \\(V\\) be a vector space and \\(W \\leq V\\) a subspace.\nThen the quotient \\(V/W\\) is the set of cosets [ v + W. ]\n\n\nTake (V = ^2) and (W = (e_1)).\nThen (V/W) is one-dimensional."
  },
